photos.description: How are you still……in my brain?

The most beautiful scene of the season:

"You have taught me that love hurts. 
You have taught me that life…. It hurts. 
And I want to be there for you, I want us to be there for each other…
So that maybe… it hurts a little less.
Alex Pearl Vause…

Will you be my partner though love and through pain and through beauty fish forever?

Alex will you marry me?"
绑架那段还戴头巾讽刺恐怖分子真是笑飞了
表白七郎，太上镜了这角色
那句话怎么说来着，站姿分攻受？
可以说是常驻搞笑担当了。
截止到EP10 Vauseman大法还在，放心放心。
这一段让我想起了第一第二季~
截止到EP10 Vauseman大法还在，放心放心。
